==English==
===Etymology===
: '''[[fanny]]''' (colloquial slang: ''[[vagina]]'') + '''[[fart]]''' (emmision of a gass)

===Noun phrase===
'''fanny fart'''
# (Colloquial slang) Noise made by the emission of air from the [[vagina]], usually associated with a physical activity such as [[horse riding]] or [[intercourse]].